8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both GrowthBar and Typli share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Short Form, Seo Tools, Templates. Where GrowthBar pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Team Collaboration, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Typli uniquely offers Tone Control and Plagiarism Check and Multilingual, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, GrowthBar holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Typli scores 5/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Typli comes in at a lower starting price of $29/mo, while GrowthBar begins at $36/mo. Typli stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. GrowthBar requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
