c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. GrowthBar is best suited for SEO blog posts, keyword research, content outlines, small teams, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Typli, meanwhile, shines for budget SEO writing, blog posts, image generation, small businesses, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2020, GrowthBar describes itself as \"SEO-focused AI writing tool with keyword research built in.\" Typli, established in 2021, positions itself as \"Affordable AI writing tool with SEO and image generation.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **GrowthBar** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (6.0 vs 5.0). However, this does not mean Typli is a poor choice — far from it. Typli excels in its own right, particularly for budget SEO writing and blog posts.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value combines ai writing with keyword research, go with GrowthBar. If good value with many features included matters more to you, Typli is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
